{"tid":1431667,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［PS4 pro club］超聯傳控球隊 9 PASS STYLE 招人（LF RF) 踢亞洲賽 AL","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:14:34.000Z","uid":78671,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4763fc36d67274b08009702eb36eb97cc70a5850","tid":1431667,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"球隊已達成最初目標，奪得了亞洲賽資格<br />\n為打造成為pro club 首支能靠傳控踢出成績的球隊<br />\n黎緊希望有更多好波之人加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現誠招可以做到在高壓迫搶下能做到護球的左右翼鋒 (LF RF)<br />\n<br />\n踢法：<br />\n球隊一直希望能做到一支踢法上模仿巴塞或曼城的傳控足球，故球隊希望球員有在隊友旁邊現位（形成三角形）幫波的意識，以及中前場球員必須擁有高控球能力（有能力在高壓迫搶下保持到控球權，比人迫兩下就甩波或者大腳就不了）<br />\n<br />\n球隊一直堅持唔踢跑狗反擊及高q大棍燒味的踢法，<br />\n雖然我都明白這兩種是pro club 最功利的踢法。<br />\n球隊希望每場都踢到能控制戰局的比賽（參考一下今年曼城（特別是主場比賽）的踢法），目標鮮明是要盡量主導球賽，而不是球來球往。<br />\n<br />\n呢一點需要邀到有共同理念及能力的選手合作才能做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每晚11點左右進行試腳（星期一至五），星期六日則視乎情況。<br />\n<br />\n如有意試腳，請add telegram <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/blackpolice_not_allowed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fblackpolice_not_allowed&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rNAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=28efa13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/blackpolice_not_allowed</a><br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc01b77b0eb8e8ad46f4a8ae25873f305eacdaf","tid":1431667,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3156ac76a13c417b77bc3d16259252f5cb3124c8","tid":1431667,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n可招埋CB / CDM / CM / CAM"},{"pid":"32592865a9c442d9b5c5aac92b47f62fdad3cfed","tid":1431667,"uid":6522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"冇用tg 有冇psn可以加？"},{"pid":"3bc8c0d7